ActAn Act to amend the statute law in relation to war veterans
PrecisOrder fixing SEPTEMBER 12 , 2003 as the day upon which paragraphs 5(a), (b), (c) and (c.1) of the DEPARTMENT OF VETERANS AFFAIRS ACT as enacted by subsection 13(2) of the Act [Bill C-41], being chapter 34 of the Statutes of Canada, 2000, shall COME INTO FORCE.
